summary: This is a brand new spell added to skyrim.
descriptionHtml:
In this spell you will notice that it sorta acts like a bomb when casted its a ball of light than when you attack someone you will notice that it explodes into fire creating a good deal of damage.
                                                    Location:
you can find this spell tomb in front of the door when you walk into breezehome just pick it up go into your inventory and learn it. Enjoyyyyyyyyyyyyyyy...........
author: austin
